Can you believe that?

00:38.690 --> 00:41.760
去吧 去找她
Go on, get your girl.

00:46.630 --> 00:48.080
LJ!
LJ!

00:48.090 --> 00:50.020
都给我马上趴下! 趴下...
Both of you face down, now!Please...

00:50.030 --> 00:53.220
