it's for my blood pressure.

01:58.890 --> 02:00.720
看看我发现了什么
Look what I found.

02:00.730 --> 02:02.780
我猜赫兰德太太很喜欢做肉饼啊
Guess Ms.Hollander liked to beat some meat.

02:02.790 --> 02:04.650
或许  让我在你太阳穴上敲几下
Maybe a couple of whacks in the temple with this oney.

02:04.660 --> 02:06.320
你就会想起钱放哪了
will help you remember where you put the m

02:06.330 --> 02:08.350
嘿 我们已经打了这混蛋一晚上了
Hey, we've been beating his ass all night.

02:08.360 --> 02:10.720
这不起什么作用
He ain't coming off the goods.

02:10.730 --> 02:12.420
我们得想些其他的办法
We need to do something different.

02:12.430 --> 02:13.950
