It don't matter what you do to me.

02:13.960 --> 02:16.820
我都不会说
I ain't talking.

02:16.830 --> 02:20.120
那好 我们是不达目的绝不罢休
Well, I ain't stopping till I get what I came for.

02:20.130 --> 02:22.720
来点音乐怎样?
How 'bout we listen to that again?

02:22.730 --> 02:25.360
噢
Oh

02:26.030 --> 02:28.280
现在你能告诉我钱在哪了吧?
now you're gonna tell me where that money is

02:28.290 --> 02:32.060
要不你就把它带进坟墓里吧
or i'm gonna read it on your tombstone?

02:32.760 --> 02:39.260
好吧...好吧 我给你点提示
okay...okay.We'll give you a little clue.

02:40.960 --> 02:44.530
钱不在这儿
It ain't here.

03:01.860 --> 03:06.590
确认了 布伦斯被逮到了
confirmed, Burrows is in custody.

03:08.990 --> 03:09.950
难以置信
Unbelievable.

03:09.960 --> 03:12.120
