He made it all the way to Arizona.

03:12.130 --> 03:14.250
再过一天 他就可以跑掉了
Another day, he would have been gone.

03:14.260 --> 03:15.250
找到马宏了吗?
You find Mahone?

03:15.260 --> 03:19.980
没 打过去都是转到语音信箱的
No.Keep trying to call, it goes straight to voicemail.

03:19.990 --> 03:21.280
我是亚历山大 马宏
This is Alexander Mahone.

03:21.290 --> 03:25.630
有事请留言
Please leave a message.

03:29.460 --> 03:30.980
金姆先生
Mr.Kim.

03:30.990 --> 03:32.780
克里曼先生
Mr.Kellerman.

03:32.790 --> 03:34.580
林肯·布伦斯被逮到了
Lincoln Burrows is in custody.

03:34.590 --> 03:36.820
这就是我为什么打电话给你
That's the reason I called.

03:36.830 --> 03:37.780
谁看着他?
Who has him?

03:37.790 --> 03:39.220
威尔科克斯 亚利桑那州的警察
Wilcox, Arizona PD.

03:39.230 --> 03:41.650
我们得马上把他弄出来
We need to extricate him, right away.

03:41.660 --> 03:43.380
马宏先生在哪?
Where's Mr.Mahone?

03:43.390 --> 03:45.180
我正在和他联系
I'm getting in touch with him right now

03:45.190 --> 03:47.820
但我自己也可应付的
but I can take care of this one myself.

03:47.830 --> 03:49.720
我们雇用马宏
This is why we hired Mr.Mahone.

03:49.730 --> 03:50.980
就因为他是这里的官方人物
He's the official face here.

03:50.990 --> 03:53.080
别担心 我不用通过官方途径
Don't worry. This won't be official,

03:53.090 --> 03:55.050
也不会有任何问题
and there won't be any questions.

03:55.060 --> 03:56.480
当然不会有问题
Of course, there will.

03:56.490 --> 04:01.860
但一定要确保他们都给我闭嘴
Just make sure no one's left to answer them.

04:12.960 --> 04:15.520
我儿子与此事无关 请放了他
My son had nothing to do with this, please.

04:15.530 --> 04:18.290
法官会做出决定的
judge will decide that.

04:18.930 --> 04:20.920
打过电话了吗?

04:20.930 --> 04:24.530
是的 菲尼克斯那边正派人过来
You call ahead? Yeah, phoenix is sending backup.

04:30.890 --> 04:34.860
我想这不是我们的人 吉米
I don't think it's one of ours, Jimmy.

04:38.690 --> 04:41.960
怎么回事?!
What the hell?!

05:08.530 --> 05:12.860
快!
come on!

05:16.160 --> 05:19.590
跑 快跑!
Run, run!

05:24.260 --> 05:25.680
过来!
Come here!

05:25.690 --> 05:28.930
好吧 冷静点
Okay, calm down.

05:30.160 --> 05:32.180
你要是敢再这样...
you y that again...

05:32.190 --> 05:33.320
你们是谁?!
who the hell are you?!

05:33.330 --> 05:35.960
我们是来帮你的!
We're on your side!

05:36.430 --> 05:39.560
我们是你父亲的人
We're with your father.

05:41.360 --> 05:44.420
马宏 林肯·布伦斯已被逮到了
Mahone, Lincoln Burrows has been apprehended.

05:44.430 --> 05:45.880
-在哪里?  -亚利桑那
Where? Arizona.

05:45.890 --> 05:48.480
我正过去 我要你也过去
I'm on my way and I need your talents, on the ground as well.

05:48.490 --> 05:49.820
我会尽快到的
I'll get there as soon as I can.

05:49.830 --> 05:52.350
我想你没听明白
I don't think you heard me.

05:52.360 --> 05:53.820
马上去亚利桑那
Get to Arizona.

05:53.830 --> 05:55.980
我就快逮到斯科菲尔德了
I'm this close to Scofield.

05:55.990 --> 05:57.980
我们有他要找的人
We have a bird in the hand.

05:57.990 --> 06:00.150
是的 我也有一个
Yeah, well, so might I.

06:00.160 --> 06:05.390
你要我找出斯科菲尔德和唐克雷蒂的会面地点
You wanted me to figure out Scofield's rendezvous with Tancredi?

06:07.230 --> 06:11.590
就在今天...
It's happening today...

06:15.790 --> 06:21.160
...我现在就在他们要来的地方
and I'm sitting right on top of it.

08:19.360 --> 08:22.790
你看什么?
what are you looking at?

08:34.130 --> 08:35.420
这是哪?
Where are we?

08:35.430 --> 08:38.050
别管是哪  这里很安全
It doesn't matter. You're safe here.

08:38.060 --> 08:40.550
请坐
You can take a seat.

08:40.560 --> 08:42.980
在没见到我爸前我不会配合
I ain't doing a thing until I see my dad.

08:42.990 --> 08:45.150
据我所知  他已经在来这儿的路上了
All I can tell you is he's on his way.

08:45.160 --> 08:46.550
他的飞机一小时后就到了
His flight lands in an hour.

08:46.560 --> 08:50.520
我为什么要相信你  女士?
Why should I trust you, lady?

08:50.530 --> 08:54.380
我看你没的选择
I don't see you have much of a choice.

08:54.390 --> 08:58.660
如果你想的话 我可以把你交还给那些警察
I could drop you back off with the cops if you'd prefer.

09:01.230 --> 09:03.520
你还有别处可去吗?
You have somewhere else to be?

09:03.530 --> 09:04.920
事实上我们是有地方去
Matter of fact, we do.

09:04.930 --> 09:06.350
你们不能走
We can't let you leave.

09:06.360 --> 09:09.450
你父亲原以为你弟弟和你在一起他人呢?
And your father was expecting your brother to be with you. Do you know where he is?

09:09.460 --> 09:12.550
你觉得我会告诉你吗?
Do you really think I'm going to answer that?

09:12.560 --> 09:17.990
你得开始和我们合作  林肯
You need to start cooperating with us, Lincoln.

09:18.060 --> 09:21.930
我们只是想帮你
We're only trying to help.

09:24.530 --> 09:29.080
迈克尔 斯科菲尔德   一周前从福克斯河州立监狱逃了出来
Micheal Scofield, escaped from Fox River a week ago

09:29.090 --> 09:31.120
没见过
No, never seen him.

09:31.130 --> 09:35.020
那如果你见到了打这个电话
Well, if you do, please call me at that number.

09:35.030 --> 09:36.880
好的
Will do.

09:36.890 --> 09:39.220
沿着路下去还有家旅店
There's another hotel down the road.

09:39.230 --> 09:42.230
谢了
Thanks.

10:22.460 --> 10:23.520
什么事?
yeah?

10:23.530 --> 10:25.550
你有份传真
You got a fax.

10:25.560 --> 10:29.260
请从门下面塞进来好吗?
Uh, could you put it under the door, please?

10:31.690 --> 10:35.090
谢谢
Thank you.

10:38.230 --> 10:42.230
一小时后  巴特菲尔德路 16781号
1 hour 16781 Butterfield Road

11:45.530 --> 11:46.920
特丽莎
Theresa.

11:46.930 --> 11:49.550
是费尔南多 苏克雷
It's Fernando Sucre.

11:49.560 --> 11:51.080
费尔南多
Fernando.

11:51.090 --> 11:52.080
特丽莎
Theresa.

11:52.090 --> 11:53.620
她不在这里
She's not here.

11:53.630 --> 11:54.650
求你别挂
Plase don't hang up.

11:54.660 --> 11:55.880
对不起...求你了
Please.

11:55.890 --> 11:58.320
