I need to know something.

11:58.330 --> 12:00.780
你现在有更麻烦的事得处理
You've got bigger problems than my sister right now.

12:00.790 --> 12:02.980
不  不  等一下  拜托
No, no. Wait. Please. Please.

12:02.990 --> 12:06.050
我必须要和她谈谈
I need to talk to her.

12:06.060 --> 12:08.180
不可能的  我们下午就走了
lease. You can't. We're leaving this afternoon.

12:08.190 --> 12:09.620
你们去哪儿?
Where you going?

12:09.630 --> 12:11.850
墨西哥的伊克斯塔帕  一周后才会回来
Ixtapa, Mexico. We won't be back for a week.

12:11.860 --> 12:14.380
也就是她和赫克特原计划度蜜月的地方
We're taking the honeymoon she had planned with Hector.

12:14.390 --> 12:16.520
过一会儿她就来接我了
he's picking me up in a few hours.

12:16.530 --> 12:19.350
-几点? -两点左右
What time? A little before 2:00

12:19.360 --> 12:21.250
你一定要让她给我打个电话
she have to call me.Okay.

12:21.260 --> 12:23.020
好吗?  我把号码给你
I'll give you the number.

12:23.030 --> 12:24.150
你现在在哪儿?
Where are you?

12:24.160 --> 12:26.050
别把我的名字写在电话号码前
Take this number off caller I.D.

12:26.060 --> 12:27.780
拜托了 特丽莎
Please, Theresa,

12:27.790 --> 12:30.720
让她给我打电话  好吗?
just have her call me, okay?

12:30.730 --> 12:34.660
我会在这里等的
I'll be right here.

14:19.630 --> 14:22.730
你好  莎拉
Hello, Sara.

14:33.610 --> 14:36.870
我都不确定你会不会来
I wasn't sure you'd come.

14:36.880 --> 14:40.380
我没得选择
I didn't have a choice.

14:40.580 --> 14:44.900
我知道这对你来说不容易
This isn't going to be easy for you

14:44.910 --> 14:46.100
你的留言说
You said in your message

14:46.110 --> 14:48.770
你有计划可以解决好这一切
that you had a plan to make this right.

14:48.780 --> 14:52.910
我想知道是什么计划
I need to know what that is.

15:01.480 --> 15:05.030
没错  她昨晚入住的
Yeah, she checked in last night.

15:05.040 --> 15:06.370
一个人?
Was she alone?

15:06.380 --> 15:09.510
是的
Yeah.

15:09.780 --> 15:11.100
凯莉 福斯特
Kelli Foster.

15:11.110 --> 15:12.430
