I put her in room nine.

15:12.440 --> 15:14.270
你是今早上想联系她的那个人?
You the guy that was trying to call this morning?

15:14.280 --> 15:16.630
早上有人想联系她?
A guy tried to call this morning?

15:16.640 --> 15:18.230
是啊  给她发了个传真
Yeah.He was trying to send her a fax.

15:18.240 --> 15:20.330
是吗?
Did he do it?

15:20.340 --> 15:22.300
是的  大概20分钟前
Yeah.20 minutes ago.

15:22.310 --> 15:23.330
你的传真机有记录吗?
Does the fax have memory?

15:23.340 --> 15:26.640
应该有
I guess so.

15:29.380 --> 15:31.970
知道这是哪儿吗?
Do you know where that is?

15:31.980 --> 15:33.430
离这里就5分钟的路
It's five minutes away.

15:33.440 --> 15:34.630
如果她回来
Hey, if she comes back,

15:34.640 --> 15:37.530
有什么要我做的吗?
is there anything you want me to do?

15:37.540 --> 15:40.570
她不会回来了
She isn't coming back.

15:40.580 --> 15:44.100
我已经安排好一起去巴拿马了
I've arranged for us to get to Panama.

15:44.110 --> 15:46.370
明天我们就去和我哥哥会合
We're meeting up with my brother tomorrow

15:46.380 --> 15:51.210
等下  这就是你的计划?
Wait.That's your plan?

15:53.240 --> 15:54.700
逃到巴拿马去?
To run away to Panama

15:54.710 --> 15:58.580
和两个美国头号通缉犯一起?
with the two most wanted men in America?

16:00.210 --> 16:02.630
迈克尔  我来是因为
Michael, I came here because

16:02.640 --> 16:04.270
我以为你会给我些象样的答案
I thought you were going to have real answers for me.

16:04.280 --> 16:07.410
这就是答案
This is an answer.

16:07.840 --> 16:10.100
这也是我们目前唯一的答案
And, right now, it's the only one we've got.

16:10.110 --> 16:15.730
和一个欺骗过我的人一起亡命天涯?
Running away into the sunset with the man who lied to me?

16:15.740 --> 16:17.200
是吗?
Really?

16:17.210 --> 16:19.530
我是说你想过其他人吗?
I mean, did you know about the other guys?

16:19.540 --> 16:21.470
你想过会把帝博格这种人
Did you know that I would be putting T-Bag

16:21.480 --> 16:23.130
放回到大街上吗?
back out on to the street?

16:23.140 --> 16:24.700
我从来也没想过会那样
I never meant for that to happen.

16:24.710 --> 16:28.030
我在做一些不得不做的事
I was doing what I needed to do.

16:28.040 --> 16:29.670
不然我哥哥就会死
My brother was going to die

16:29.680 --> 16:33.040
可我父亲已经死了
Well, my father's dead

16:44.440 --> 16:49.940
你父亲的事我很抱歉
I am sorry about your father.

16:50.810 --> 16:52.800
对许多事情 我都感到很抱歉
I'm sorry for a lot of things.

16:52.810 --> 16:55.940
对于你的那些事
For what I did to you.

16:57.210 --> 17:00.100
我有很多很多的悔恨
I have many, many regrets

17:00.110 --> 17:01.770
但那是最后悔的一个
but that's the biggest.

17:01.780 --> 17:05.480
这已经于事无补了
it does not help me right now

17:07.680 --> 17:13.080
这点我也很抱歉
I'm sorry for that, too.

17:13.610 --> 17:16.800
我并不指望你...
I didn't expect you to, uh...

17:16.810 --> 17:19.770
我并不指望你能原谅我
I didn't expect you forgive me.

17:19.780 --> 17:23.730
但是我不想让你...
But I don't want you, to, uh...

17:23.740 --> 17:28.810
不想让你独自来面对这一切
I don't want you to be alone in this.

17:38.940 --> 17:42.740
我不想独自面对
I don't want to be alone.

17:49.740 --> 17:51.700
我们走吧  快上车
let's go. get into the car

17:51.710 --> 17:54.470
我们出不去了
You can't get out this way.

17:54.480 --> 17:55.870
迈克尔 这是唯一一条出去的路
Go back is the only way out of here

17:55.880 --> 17:58.580
我们就从这条路离开这里
That is where we are going.

18:14.580 --> 18:15.770
坐稳了
Hold on.just hold on

