-迈克尔你想干什么? -你坐稳就行了
Micheal, what r u doing? just hold on

18:52.780 --> 18:54.300
你还好吗?
You all right?

18:54.500 --> 18:57.740
他还在跟着我们
He's still behind us.

19:05.680 --> 19:08.180
坐稳了
hold on

19:48.480 --> 19:51.310
站起来  拜格威尔
On your feet, Bagwell.

19:53.740 --> 19:57.540
看上去很热哦
Skewers are hot.

20:01.380 --> 20:03.980
他有把钥匙!
he's got a key

20:11.140 --> 20:15.980
我会拿到钥匙的  别逼我...
I'm going to get that key if I have to...

20:33.910 --> 20:35.970
我们马上就会见到那钥匙了老兄
we're going to see that key again, friend.

20:35.980 --> 20:39.440
马上就会见到它
We're going to see it real soon.

20:41.840 --> 20:44.170
把信用卡还给我
Give me my credit card.

20:44.180 --> 20:48.440
你都买了些什么?
What did you get me?

20:49.240 --> 20:50.670
买了些什么?
What did you get?

20:50.680 --> 20:52.300
李子汁 烟叶
Prune juice, smokes

20:52.310 --> 20:53.830
